latestIgtvVideos.title: Summer Subtle Look.✨🤍
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
This summer, wear your confidence with shiny eyes and subtle cheeks and lips! Loved how the makeup literally gave the dress a different look. Tell me how you guys like it!❤️So without wasting much time of yours here are some tips and the product details.

Tips:
1. Don’t use this amount of concealer every time you get ready. I don’t usually use concealer much but I had some extra spots this time, so I had to. 
2. If you use this amount of concealer, make sure you don’t use the regular amount of foundation on your skin. Lessen the amount of foundation and you’ve balanced it.
3. Always use a primer to prep your skin. If you don’t have a primer, go for Aloe-Vera gel. It works just fine. I forgot to shoot that part but it’s always necessary to apply it on your skin.
4. And last but not the least, don’t cake your face with too much powder. In fact apply a thin layer or loose powder on your skin. Don’t use it too much.
5. And the details of the products used:
~Face serum : @seboncare from @amazondotin 
.
 ~Concealer : @lagirlcosmetics
.
~Mousse Foundation: @lakmeindia in the shade ‘Ivory Fair’ 01
.
~Moisturiser : Peach Milk @lakmeindia
.
~Loose Powder : Rose Powder with SPF @lakmeindia 
.
~Eyeshadow Palette : Sundowner Stunner @mynykaa 
.
~Liquid Eyeliner : @lakmeindia
.
~Blush : 
Peachy shade by @hilaryrhodacosmetics

~Wonder puff cushion lipstick in the shade : ‘Born to Blossom’ @mynykaa 
.
~Highlighter Stick : @swissbeautycosmetics in the shade 05 Golden from @mynykaa 
.
~Crayon Lipstick : @mynykaa in the shade ‘Like to Mauve it’ 14
.
~Water Tint : ‘Pink Mate’ 02 @mynykaa 
.
~Kajal : @lorealparis
.
